HEADWORD: Pandowdy
<hw>Pan*dow"dy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A deep pie or
pudding made of baked apples, or of sliced bread and apples baked
together, with no bottom crust.</def>⟦br⟧
